org.cyclops.cyclopscore.ingredient.collection

Interface IIngredientSetMutable<T,M>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The instance type.
    M - The matching condition parameter.
    All Superinterfaces:
    IIngredientCollection<T,M>, IIngredientCollectionLike<T,M,T>, IIngredientCollectionMutable<T,M>, IIngredientSet<T,M>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IngredientHashSet, IngredientSet, IngredientTreeSet

    public interface IIngredientSetMutable<T,M>
extends IIngredientSet<T,M>, IIngredientCollectionMutable<T,M>
    A mutable ingredient collection using set semantics. This means that each instances can only be present once in the collection based on its equals method.
